TenantSecurityTenantInfo.name: TenantSecurityTenantInfo
TenantSecurityTenantInfo.description: Stores information on changes related to the tenant history.

DetailIdentifier.description: The unique identifier for this record.

Instance.description: The instance that the tenant is being hosted on.

MyDomainName.description: The name of the domain for this tenant.

Name.description: The name of the metric for which the data is being collected.

SandboxAlias.description: The alias specified by the user when the user creates a Sandbox.

SandboxType.description: The type specified by the user when the user creates a Sandbox.

Status.description: The status of the tenant. For example, active or inactive.

TenantName.description: The name of the tenant (org) that this record is for.

TenantType.description: The type of tenant in this org.
